{"word":"ἀναθεματίζω","slug":"ἀναθεματίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναθεματίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀνάθεμα'><el>ἀνάθεμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to devote</i>, <el>ἀναθέματι ἀν. ἑαυτούς</el> <i>to bind</i> themselves <i>by a curse</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to swear</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}